                \displaystyle\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(a_n\cos nx \sin mx + b_n\sin nx \sin mx)\} dx$<br>
                $\displaystyle(右辺)=\displaystyle\frac{a_0}{2} \int_{-\pi}^{\pi} \sin mx dx +
                \displaystyle\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(a_n\int_{-\pi}^{\pi} \cos nx \sin mx dx + b_n\int_{-\pi}^{\pi} \sin nx \sin mx dx)\}$<br>
