                $\displaystyle a_n = \frac{1}{\pi} \int_{-\pi}^{\pi} f(x) \cos mx dx$<br>
                $\displaystyle b_n = \frac{1}{\pi} \int_{-\pi}^{\pi} f(x) \sin mx dx$<br>
